a.issue(href="http://github.com/jsbin/jsbin/issues/new") Problem? Feedback? Let us know!

for category in categories
  div(class="category #{category.name}")
    h2 #{category.title}
    h4 #{category.description}
    != partial('../_partials/help-posts', { filter: category.name })

div(class="category")
  h2 Legals
  h4 Our terms and privacy policy that we run JS Bin under
  ul.links
    li
      a(href="/legals/privacy") Privacy Policy
    li
      a(href="/legals") Terms of Service